{"id":4180,"date":"2025-06-16T13:50:49","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:50:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4180"},"modified":"2025-06-16T13:50:49","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:50:49","slug":"huong-dan-cach-dung-sua-rua-mat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/huong-dan-cach-dung-sua-rua-mat\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. \u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/huong-dan-cach-dung-sua-rua-mat\/\"><b><i>c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t<\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap da m\u1eb7t lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"6-buoc-cach-dung-sua-rua-mat-hieu-qua-de-lan-da-sach-sau\"><\/span><b>6 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Bi\u1ebft <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, h\u00e3y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo 6 b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4181\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4181\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4181\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-1.webp\" alt=\"6 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4181\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">6 b\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-1-%e2%80%93-ve-sinh-tay-va-de-toc-gon-gang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1 &#8211; V\u1ec7 sinh tay v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f3c g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, h\u00e3y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00f3c g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00f3c b\u1ecb \u01b0\u1edbt ho\u1eb7c d\u00ednh s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, v\u1ec7 sinh tay s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u1edbi x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u1eeb tay l\u00e2y lan l\u00ean da m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-2-%e2%80%93-lam-uot-da-mat-voi-nuoc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2 &#8211; L\u00e0m \u01b0\u1edbt da m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u01b0\u1edbt da m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng gi\u00e3n n\u1edf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t trong s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 c\u1eb7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. L\u01b0u \u00fd, n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean \u1edf nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 kho\u1ea3ng 37\u00b0C, tr\u00e1nh n\u01b0\u1edbc qu\u00e1 n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-3-%e2%80%93-su-dung-sua-rua-mat-gel\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3 &#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t gel<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cho m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0o l\u00f2ng b\u00e0n tay v\u00e0 xoa nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt. L\u1edbp b\u1ecdt c\u00e0ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 bong b\u00f3ng c\u00e0ng nh\u1ecf, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ebd th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, l\u1edbp b\u1ecdt m\u1ecbn s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m ma s\u00e1t, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-4-%e2%80%93-massage-nhe-nhang-lam-sach-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4 &#8211; Massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thoa b\u1ecdt l\u00ean da m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay \u0111\u1ec3 massage nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng theo chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00f2n t\u1eeb trong ra ngo\u00e0i. Massage kho\u1ea3ng 1 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n ra ngo\u00e0i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-5-%e2%80%93-rua-sach-da-voi-nuoc\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5 &#8211; R\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch da v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sau khi massage, d\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean da. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i b\u1ecdt s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-6-%e2%80%93-tham-kho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 6 &#8211; Th\u1ea5m kh\u00f4 da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, d\u00f9ng kh\u0103n m\u1ec1m ho\u1eb7c b\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y trang \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5m kh\u00f4 da m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng. Tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-khi-dung-sua-rua-mat-de-cham-soc-da-hieu-qua\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd khi d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-sua-rua-mat-bao-nhieu-lanngay\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u khuy\u00ean b\u1ea1n n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y, v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4182\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4182\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4182 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-2.webp\" alt=\"D\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4182\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">D\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t bao nhi\u00eau l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i: V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba m\u00e0 da ti\u1ebft ra trong su\u1ed1t \u0111\u00eam, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. V\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, gi\u00fap da th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong ng\u00e0y (n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n): N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1ed5 m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 2 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xen k\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ea1ch thay v\u00ec s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4, bong tr\u00f3c, ho\u1eb7c d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng, h\u00e3y h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng 1 l\u1ea7n\/ng\u00e0y v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nen-chon-sua-rua-mat-dang-nao\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c nhau, v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa d\u1ea1ng gel hay kem ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4183\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4183\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4183\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-3.webp\" alt=\"N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/67-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4183\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n, s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng gel l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng gel gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u00edt t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf k\u00edch \u1ee9ng da v\u00e0 gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trang \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trang \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u. S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t, gi\u00fap da s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"sua-rua-mat-gsc-55-ph-cleansing-gel\"><\/span><b>S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng l\u00e0 S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 pH l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng 5.5, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb l\u00e1 tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, c\u00e1m g\u1ea1o, m\u00eda \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0nh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean kh\u00e1c, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4031\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4031\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4031\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp\" alt=\"D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4031\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m cho da, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, paraben, x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, hay SLS, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho da, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 v\u00f9ng da m\u1ecfng nh\u01b0 da m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00ean, GSC hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 <\/span><b><i>c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t<\/i><\/b> <span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y v\u1edbi s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd chia s\u1ebb nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u00fap da m\u1eb7t lu\u00f4n s\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4184,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4180","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4180","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4180"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4180\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4185,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4180\/revisions\/4185"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4184"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4180"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4180"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4180"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}